{"tid":905656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國公司首創「自慰假」（Self-love days），鼓勵員工喺假期能夠盡情touch myself，享受性愛高潮！","createTime":"2018-11-17T10:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:58:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c504a95686f34677f18aa187f0e049233bf8bc1","tid":905656,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2614882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2614882&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=cdc8b993\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2614882&h=b75b6e41\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2614882</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/officialchapmanto/photos/a.657815361024154/1259868470818837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fofficialchapmanto%2Fphotos%2Fa.657815361024154%2F1259868470818837&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=d3a201ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/officialchapmanto/photos/a.657815361024154/1259868470818837</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/46288077_1259868477485503_2042341654593011712_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=b09a1d40b28e6bb0032dd6c64474bda9&amp;oe=5C83A413\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F46288077_1259868477485503_2042341654593011712_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Db09a1d40b28e6bb0032dd6c64474bda9%26oe%3D5C83A413&h=8f2ab9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多企業都會提供員工病假、產假、生理假，不過英國卻有一間公司還開放讓員工請自慰假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為企業認為，自慰不但讓員工更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、紓壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，還可以提高生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpU4bsJZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpU4bsJZ.jpg&h=260274a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，英國情趣商品公司「LELO UK」最近推出一種特別的員工福利，讓員工有額外4天假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。公司將這4天的假稱為「自愛假」（self love day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），員工可以請假在家裡自慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為公司認為自慰可以提升員工生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fRhLAg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fRhLAg.gif&h=6c78d537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「LELO UK」還針對自慰的益處進行了一份調查，調查對象包括超過2000名英國人。結果發現有78%的人認為性高潮（包含自慰與性愛）能為他們帶來開心。有66%的人表示，高潮後讓他們更有生產力，還有40%的人更認為，性高潮導致的快樂、生產力提升，最多可維持到5天。"},{"pid":"39b347606859880212cf65e494407995aedd1376","tid":905656,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:01:11.000Z","msg":"點解要成日"},{"pid":"6e6d2fd06c452e2dcbda3a2d2463ac75114f076f","tid":905656,"uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"「LELO UK」發言人娜索佛（Rachael Nsofor）表示，他們認為性滿足是人們的基本權益，而且還是完全免費的。因此公司希望讓員工利用這些假日去探索他們的快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、從事讓他們感到刺激的事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，等員工隔天回來上班<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，也會更有生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友看到這樣的自愛假後都笑翻，「但要怎麼向老闆開口？」、「我以為能有午休就很棒了！」也有網友幽默表示，「如果你需要花一整天自慰，那你應該有些地方搞錯了。」、「其實只要午休時間就能解決了啊。」"},{"pid":"65798c3d17d32909665e1ce77f1d28cdce56b6ac","tid":905656,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"<i